metadata.name: Beginning of the search
metadata.description:
This is 1 NFT in a collection of 10 photographs that have been issued as a single, unique edition.

Photo: 6670x10000 px

Man lives in space. Things are man's companions, and they, too, are in space.

Certain things are peculiar to each stage of human life, but stages replace each other, and things remain, filling up space.

And at some point in our lives, we realize that in order to move on, we need more space or fewer things.

But it can be hard to say goodbye to things that have been your companions for a certain period of life, just as it can be hard to say goodbye to people close to you.

A person is looking for a way out.
